author: lhazlewood
msg: SHIRO-112 - ShiroException - removed unnecessary 'implements Serializable' clause because all Throwables are Serializable.  SimplePrincipalCollection - iimplemented Serialization readObject/writeObject methods to mitigate serialization problems resulting from implementation changes.  This should allow most implementation changes to occur without affecting application end-users (e.g. no rememberMe cookie breakage).
